@startuml
autonumber
title "System Sequence Diagram - US24 : Load Game Progress"
actor "Player" as Player
participant ":System" as System

activate Player

Player -> System: requests to load saved game progress
activate System
System --> Player: displays list of saved games with details (timestamp, progress, etc.)
deactivate System

Player -> System: selects saved game to load
activate System
System --> Player: displays selected game details (budget, time, etc.)
System --> Player: displays operation success
System --> Player: restores game state
deactivate System

@enduml
